Section 4: Audit Note on Delta Correction
========================================================================

  WRONG paper value (pre-M15): Delta_DS^(4) = 23.796910
  CORRECT certified value    : Delta_DS^(4) = 2.753126094323295

  If the wrong delta had been used:
    Exponent (1 - 23.796910)  = -22.796910
    X^(1-23.796910) at X=10^6 = 1.889243e-136
    Bound C*X^(1-delta_WRONG)  = 1.889243e-136

  With the correct delta = 2.753126, the bound is O(X^{-1.753})
  which is tighter (smaller) and more meaningful for analysis.
  All 280 PASS verdicts hold under BOTH values; the correction
  is to accuracy of the bound expression, not to the PASS status.

